data.description: ASSUMABLE 3.75% FHA LOAN!  This welcoming home sits on the corner of a cul de sac, in the highly desired community of Wingfield Springs.  The open concept, split floor plan houses four, generously sized bedrooms and an office.  The high ceilings add to the open feel, where you will enjoy time with friends and family, and feel just as comfortable spending time on your own! The perfect size!  Outside, you'll love the beautifully landscaped yard, that truly feels like a sanctuary! Gated RV parking, plus a second access for your trailer or SXS!  Lots of extra concrete and pavers put the finishing touch on this lovely yard.  The spa/hot tub and kitchen appliances are all just about two years new and stay convey with the home!  Updated and beautiful, this home is waiting for a new owner.  See it, Love it, Make it your new address.  Looks like opportunity is knocking on your door!  Listing agent is related to sellers.
